casebody.data:
Owen D. Leavitt
v.
State of North Carolina No. 192P16 Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 9, 2016 Owen D. Leavitt, for Leavitt, Owen D. Kimberly N. Callahan, Assistant Attorney General, Sarah Kirkman, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Petitioner on the 19th of May 2016 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Alexander County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 9th of June 2016."

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 19th of May 2016 by Petitioner to Proceed In Forma Pauperis:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference, this the 9th of June 2016."
